FBIS3-36810 "drsov028_a_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Parties React to NATO Decision on Bosnia Zhirinovskiy Warns Countries LD0902182194 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1700 GMT 9 Feb 94 LD0902182194 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, leader of the Liberal Democratic Party of Russia, shocked the public again today by telling journalists at the State Duma that if any bombing raids are conducted against Bosnia his party and State Duma deputies would force the Russian Government to bomb and destroy the country that sent its aircraft.
